                                 @{bg fill} @{fg shine}@{b}>>> CED_HTML v2.2 <<<@{ub}@{fg text} @{bg background}
                                       19-Mar-1999


A set of AREXX scripts to help writing HTML v3.2 documents with CygnusED v4.2.


    1. @{" Introduction             "  link "introduction" } What is it for?

    2. @{" Status                   "  link "status"       } It's free!
    3. @{" Requirements             "  link "requirements" } Amiga, AREXX, CED v4.2+...
    4. @{" Installation             "  link "installation" } How to beam CED_HTML to your hardrive

    5. @{" Usage                    "  link "usage"        } How to use this package

       5.01 @{" Main structure      " link "structure" } <HTML><HEAD><META...></HEAD> <BODY..>...
       5.02 @{" Title               " link "title"     } <H1> ... <H6 ALIGN="...">
       5.03 @{" Font options        " link "font"      } <FONT SIZE="..." COLOR="...">
       5.04 @{" Text aspect         " link "aspect"    } <I>, <B>, <U>, <SUB>, <SMALL>, <CODE>,...
       5.05 @{" Paragraph           " link "paragraph" } <P ALIGN="...">...</P>
       5.06 @{" Sub paragraph       " link "sub"       } <DIV ALIGN="...">
       5.07 @{" List structure      " link "list"      } <UL> or <OL TYPE="..." START="..."><LI>...
